pokedexEntries.red: The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws the bone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets.
pokedexEntries.blue: The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws the bone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets.
pokedexEntries.yellow: Small and weak, this Pokémon is adept with its Bone Club. It has grown more vicious over the ages.
pokedexEntries.gold: It has been seen pounding boulders with the bone it carries in order to tap out messages to others.
pokedexEntries.silver: It collects bones from an unknown place. A Marowak graveyard exists somewhere in the world, rumors say.
pokedexEntries.crystal: Somewhere in the world is a cemetery just for Marowak. It gets its bones from those graves.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has overcome its sadness at the loss of its mother and grown tough. This Pokémon's tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has overcome its sadness at the loss of its mother and grown tough. This Pokémon's tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken.
pokedexEntries.emerald: A Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has grown tough by overcoming the grief of losing its mother. Its tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It is small and was originally very weak. Its temperament turned ferocious when it began using bones.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws the bone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets.
pokedexEntries.diamond: From its birth, this savage Pokémon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons.
pokedexEntries.pearl: From its birth, this savage Pokémon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons.
pokedexEntries.platinum: From its birth, this savage Pokémon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: It has been seen pounding boulders with the bone it carries in order to tap out messages to others.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: It collects bones from an unknown place. Some whisper that a Marowak graveyard exists somewhere in the world.
pokedexEntries.black: From its birth, this savage Pokémon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons.
pokedexEntries.white: From its birth, this savage Pokémon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons.
pokedexEntries.black2: From its birth, this savage Pokémon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons.
pokedexEntries.white2: From its birth, this savage Pokémon constantly holds bones. It is skilled in using them as weapons.
pokedexEntries.x: It is small and was originally very weak. Its temperament turned ferocious when it began using bones.
pokedexEntries.y: The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws the bone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets.
pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has overcome its sadness at the loss of its mother and grown tough. This Pokemon's tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has overcome its sadness at the loss of its mother and grown tough. This Pokemon's tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken.
pokedexEntries.sun: Originally, it was weak and timid. After evolution, its temperament becomes violent, and it begins to wield bones as weapons.
pokedexEntries.moon: This Pokémon is out for vengeance on its natural enemy, Mandibuzz. It throws bones like boomerangs to try to take it down.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: It throws bones at Mandibuzz to knock it down. It’s thought that Marowak is trying to avenge its parent.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: They thump their bones rhythmically to communicate among themselves. There are nearly 50 different rhythmic patterns.
